codex
Implemented the Node.js/Express file-storage app with:

- User registration/login using SQLite-backed users and sessions
- File uploads to disk under `data/files/`
- Per-user folders
- Download and delete for owned files
- Share link creation, public read/download access, and revocation
- SQLite metadata in `data/app.db`
- `package.json`, `.gitignore`, and README run instructions for port `5082`

I did not run or install anything, per the workspace instructions. The app is ready to run with:

```bash
npm install
npm start
```
